WEBVTT

08:55.409 --> 08:57.662
What is the spiciest chili?

08:57.745 --> 08:58.788
This one.

09:02.792 --> 09:04.001
Go ahead, taste them.

09:04.085 --> 09:06.003
They don't look that spicy.

09:24.689 --> 09:25.773
Spicy.

09:28.359 --> 09:30.152
Yes, spicy.

09:39.203 --> 09:40.705
Do you have sweet betel like this?

09:40.788 --> 09:43.583
In India, we a have sweet one.
It's very delicious.

09:43.666 --> 09:45.334
No, we don't have that here.

09:47.044 --> 09:49.130
Okay, this one.

22:21.673 --> 22:26.178
-May I stir it a little?
-It is not allowed.

22:29.556 --> 22:32.517
Come on, what are you so afraid of?

22:32.601 --> 22:34.728
Fine, okay.

22:37.314 --> 22:39.816
Take a look.
It is better if you make a figure eight.

22:39.900 --> 22:42.027
See how I make an eight this way?

22:42.110 --> 22:45.197
It will not burn if you do it this way.

22:45.280 --> 22:48.450
It will never burn.
You just have to make a figure eight.
